<sect2>
<title>Installation of <application>libxslt</application></title>

<para>Install <application>libxslt</application> by running the following commands:</para>

<screen><userinput><command>./configure --prefix=/usr &amp;&amp;
make &amp;&amp;
make install</command></userinput></screen>

<!--
<tip><title>Upgrade Hint</title><para>You may wish to remove the old
documentation directories for <application>libxslt</application> in <filename>/usr/share/doc</filename>.</para></tip>
-->

</sect2>

